072   * @param ownerType the {@link Type} that owns this {@link
073   * DefaultParameterizedType}; may be (and usually is) {@code null};
074   * if non-{@code null} is most commonly a {@link Class} as in all
075   * JDKs through at least 13
076   *
077   * @param rawType the raw type; must not be {@code null}; is most commonly a {@link Class} as in all

079   *
080   * @param actualTypeArguments the actual {@linkplain
081   * #getActualTypeArguments() actual type arguments} of this {@link

083   *
084   * @exception NullPointerException if {@code rawType} is {@code

087  public DefaultParameterizedType(final Type ownerType, final Type rawType, final Type... actualTypeArguments) {
088    super();
089    this.ownerType = ownerType;
090    this.rawType = Objects.requireNonNull(rawType);
091    this.actualTypeArguments = actualTypeArguments == null ? EMPTY_TYPE_ARRAY : actualTypeArguments;
092    this.hashCode = this.computeHashCode();
093  }

129  private final int computeHashCode() {
130    int hashCode = 17;
131
132    final Object ownerType = this.getOwnerType();
133    int c = ownerType == null ? 0 : ownerType.hashCode();
134    hashCode = 37 * hashCode + c;
135
136    final Object rawType = this.getRawType();
137    c = rawType == null ? 0 : rawType.hashCode();
138    hashCode = 37 * hashCode + c;
139
140    final Type[] actualTypeArguments = this.getActualTypeArguments();
141    c = Arrays.hashCode(actualTypeArguments);
142    hashCode = 37 * hashCode + c;
143
144    return hashCode;
145  }

147  @Override
148  public final boolean equals(final Object other) {
149    if (other == this) {
150      return true;
151    } else if (other instanceof ParameterizedType) {
152      final ParameterizedType her = (ParameterizedType)other;
153
154      final Object ownerType = this.getOwnerType();
155      if (ownerType == null) {
156        if (her.getOwnerType() != null) {
157          return false;
158        }
159      } else if (!ownerType.equals(her.getOwnerType())) {
160        return false;
161      }
162
163      final Object rawType = this.getRawType();
164      if (rawType == null) {
165        if (her.getRawType() != null) {
166          return false;
167        }
168      } else if (!rawType.equals(her.getRawType())) {
169        return false;
170      }
171
172      final Type[] actualTypeArguments = this.getActualTypeArguments();
173      if (!Arrays.equals(actualTypeArguments, her.getActualTypeArguments())) {
174        return false;
175      }
176
177      return true;
178    } else {
179      return false;
180    }

183  @Override
184  public String toString() {
185    final StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
186    final Type rawType = this.getRawType();
187    final Type ownerType = this.getOwnerType();
188    if (ownerType == null) {
189      sb.append(rawType.getTypeName());
190    } else {
191      sb.append(ownerType.getTypeName()).append("$");
192      if (ownerType instanceof ParameterizedType) {
193        final ParameterizedType ownerPType = (ParameterizedType)ownerType;
194        final Type ownerRawType = ownerPType.getRawType();
195        sb.append(rawType.getTypeName().replace(ownerRawType.getTypeName() + "$", ""));
196      } else if (rawType instanceof Class) {
197        sb.append(((Class<?>)rawType).getSimpleName());
198      } else {
199        sb.append(rawType.getTypeName());
200      }
201    }
202
203    final Type[] actualTypeArguments = this.getActualTypeArguments();
204    if (actualTypeArguments != null && actualTypeArguments.length > 0) {
205      final StringJoiner stringJoiner = new StringJoiner(", ", "<", ">");
206      stringJoiner.setEmptyValue("");
207      for (final Type actualTypeArgument : actualTypeArguments) {
208        stringJoiner.add(actualTypeArgument.getTypeName());
209      }
210      sb.append(stringJoiner.toString());
211    }
212    return sb.toString();
213  }

215  private final void readObject(final ObjectInputStream stream) throws ClassNotFoundException, IOException {
216    stream.defaultReadObject();
217    final Object ownerType = stream.readObject();
218    if (ownerType == null) {
219      this.ownerType = null;
220    } else if (ownerType instanceof Type) {
221      this.ownerType = (Type)ownerType;
222    } else {
223      throw new IOException(new IllegalArgumentException("ownerType: " + ownerType));
224    }
225    final Object rawType = stream.readObject();
226    if (rawType == null) {
227      throw new IOException(new NullPointerException("rawType"));
228    } else if (rawType instanceof Type) {
229      this.rawType = (Type)rawType;
230    } else {
231      throw new IOException(new IllegalArgumentException("rawType: " + rawType));
232    }
233    final Object actualTypeArguments = stream.readObject();
234    assert actualTypeArguments instanceof Serializable[];
235    final Serializable[] serializableActualTypeArguments = (Serializable[])actualTypeArguments;
236    if (serializableActualTypeArguments == null || serializableActualTypeArguments.length <= 0) {
237      this.actualTypeArguments = EMPTY_TYPE_ARRAY;
238    } else {
239      this.actualTypeArguments = new Type[serializableActualTypeArguments.length];
240      System.arraycopy(serializableActualTypeArguments, 0, this.actualTypeArguments, 0, serializableActualTypeArguments.length);
241    }
242    this.hashCode = this.computeHashCode();
243  }

245  private final void writeObject(final ObjectOutputStream stream) throws IOException {
246    stream.defaultWriteObject();
247    stream.writeObject(Types.toSerializableType(this.getOwnerType()));
248    stream.writeObject(Types.toSerializableType(this.getRawType()));
249    final Type[] actualTypeArguments = this.getActualTypeArguments();
250    if (actualTypeArguments == null || actualTypeArguments.length <= 0) {
251      stream.writeObject(new Serializable[0]);
252    } else {
253      final Serializable[] newTypeArguments = new Serializable[actualTypeArguments.length];
254      for (int i = 0; i < newTypeArguments.length; i++) {
255        newTypeArguments[i] = Types.toSerializableType(actualTypeArguments[i]);
256      }
257      stream.writeObject(newTypeArguments);
258    }
259  }
